               <msContents>
                  <summary>Sword of the Trinity, ሠይፈ፡ ሥላሴ፡; Prayer to God: “For the Sake of the Honor and Covenant of Our Lady, Virgin Mary,” በእንተ፡ ዕበያ፡ ወክብራ፡ ወኪዳና፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="69v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT2296Sayfas"/>
                     <note>Arranged for days of the week (Monday, <locus target="#1r"/>; Tuesday, <locus target="#10v"/>; ‎Wednesday, <locus target="#20v"/>; Thursday, <locus target="#29r"/>; Friday, <locus target="#38v"/>; Saturday, <locus target="#50r"/>; ‎daily, <locus target="#55r"/> [an error]; Sunday, <locus target="#57v"/>; daily, <locus target="#63v"/>)‎</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="69v" to="73v"/>
                     <title>Prayer to God: “For the Sake of the Honor and Covenant of Our Lady, Virgin Mary,” <foreign xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ዕበያ፡ ወክብራ፡ ወኪዳና፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል።</foreign>
